# Redirects from the old AgentMethods-hosted site to the migrated site.
#
# IMPORTANT: Cloudflare Pages automatically serves clean URLs for any
# .html file (e.g. a request for /about-us.html gets a built-in 308 to
# /about-us, which then serves about-us.html). Because of that, every
# extensionless old URL (e.g. /long-term-care-ltc-insurance/fact-vs-fiction-
# about-long-term-care-insurance) already resolves to the correct current
# page with NO redirect rule needed here. Do not add rules that redirect
# an extensionless path to its .html equivalent -- that fights the
# platform's own canonical redirect and creates an infinite loop.
#
# Only the old CMS "/home/*" section needs explicit rules, since nothing
# on the current site lives under /home/.
/home/about-us     /about-us    301
/home/contact-us    /contact     301
/home/newsletters   /articles    301
/home/*             /            301
